These are Puzzles for 1x4 Level 3

.:: Puzzle 1x4-Level-3-1::.
The people prefer 4 different types of sport: weightlifting, handball, volleyball, parkour
1. the person who's sport is weightlifting is on the far left##1
2. the person who's sport is handball is on the left or right of the person who's sport is weightlifting##3
3. the person who's sport is handball is on the left or right of the person who's sport is volleyball##3

.:: Answer ::.
|        |     1     |     2     |  3   |   4    |
| Sport   | weightlifting | handball | volleyball | parkour |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 1x4-Level-3-2::.
The people's birthday is in 4 different months: march, january, december, august
1. the person who's birthday is in march is on the right of the person who's birthday is in january##1
2. the person who's birthday is in august is on the left of the person who's birthday is in december##1
3. the person who's birthday is in december is on the far left or far right##3

.:: Answer ::.
|            |   1   |   2    |   3   |    4     |
| Birthday   | january | march | august | december |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 1x4-Level-3-3::.
The people use 4 different means of transport: helicopter, quad-bike, motorbike, train
1. the person driving the quad-bike is on the left of the person driving the train##1
2. the person driving the helicopter is on the far left or far right##3
3. the person driving the train is on the far right##1

.:: Answer ::.
|         |   1    |    2    |     3      |    4    |
| Transport   | helicopter | motorbike | quad-bike | train |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 1x4-Level-3-4::.
There are 4 different favourite colors: brown, orange, yellow, coral
1. the person who likes yellow is on the far right##1
2. the person who likes yellow is on the right of the person who likes coral##1
3. the person who likes brown is on the left or right of the person who likes coral##3

.:: Answer ::.
|               |    1    |     2     |     3     |  4  |
| Color   | orange | brown | coral | yellow |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 1x4-Level-3-5::.
The people have 4 different hobbies: drawing, rock-climbing, video-games, magic-tricks
1. the person who's hobby is drawing is on the far left or far right##3
2. the person who's hobby is rock-climbing is on the right of the person who's hobby is video-games##1
3. the person who's hobby is drawing is on the right of the person who's hobby is rock-climbing##1

.:: Answer ::.
|         |       1       |    2    |  3   |     4      |
| Hobby   | magic-tricks | video-games | rock-climbing | drawing |

