.:: Puzzle 1x4-Level-3-10::.
4 different games are played: whist, chess, snooker, bridge
1. the person playing chess is on the right of the person playing bridge##1
2. the person playing chess is between the person playing whist and the person playing bridge##2
3. the person playing whist is on the left or right of the person playing snooker##3
4. the person playing whist is on the left or right of the person playing snooker##3

.:: Answer ::.
|        |     1      |    2     |    3    |    4    |
| Game   | bridge | chess | whist | snooker |

